I looked for you and called your name but you didn't answer me so after five or ten minutes I decided to just go home. When I pulled into the trailer park I saw your coat and shoes on the floor of the truck. I was gonna drive back up there but I didn't want to miss wrestle mania 216, rump ranger rick vs randy the ratchet jaw penis snatcher.
